snippet.title: ChildStory Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: As a child, we all wondered: "Where does the Moon disappear every month?". This childstory will tell about Sonya, a girl in a purple kigurumi and about the angry Heavenly shepherdess Nora. It is the two of them who create the cycle of the appearance and the loss of the Moon.
